{"tid":1169652,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"星期五收工後節目一覽","createTime":"2019-05-24T13:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T05:46:54.000Z","uid":193138,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bad9c3bfcc8c0669015fb5ed8748ed0480081654","tid":1169652,"uid":193138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"6點準時打卡走人<br />\n趁人少行個圈食個飯<br />\n再衝返屋企睇倚天屠龍記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完9點半岩岩好可以睇埋達哥，睇到11點半就趕尾班車去羅湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後唔洗講過關打的按個摸<br />\n訓醒又一個美好星期六<br />\n識食一定係中午食海底撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為唔洗排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完就去唱K，唱到夜晚又去按個摸<br />\n訓醒搭火車直接落沙田馬場買馬仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n羊左錢就買埋個pizza hut 至返屋企<br />\n咁又一個happy weekend <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d40e0966428ba7529c25648de73e90bea1bda3","tid":1169652,"uid":193138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"邊個柒頭偷偷留下負評"},{"pid":"7a7db2e4563718e0879e0f0f3b913e33bb483e6e","tid":1169652,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b5ec696242ddc6f1199cf2c144a3bafab601b2","tid":1169652,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:12:25.000Z","msg":"Very nice"},{"pid":"125813d5b8227877be14fce26fc9748f297192d6","tid":1169652,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"豬錢呢"},{"pid":"5eb951b2e489c90c91d328d9a3dd9862a6a34e25","tid":1169652,"uid":193138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"125813d5b8227877be14fce26fc9748f297192d6","tid":1169652,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:13:41